table: A general dialog agent, whose role can be set by system prompt.
A dictionary version dialog agent, who responds in Python dictionary format.
An agent that can write and execute Python code.
An agent that generates images according to the requirements.

RpcDialogAgent

references: Pre-built Agent Templates:          As cataloged in Table                  1                , AgentScope offers pre-built agents and ready-to-use components for tasks like dialogue management, user proxying, multi-modal data handling, and distributed deployment. These templates serve as starting points for developers to customize and extend, significantly accelerating the development of multi-agent LLM applications.
